                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">讲得超清楚。就是明明是讲佛教僧人犯法的，标题取这么大。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="726120712">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-726120712" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-726120712" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="726120712">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/kyo_nana/">堪堪</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-09-08</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">读到影响审判因素一章，很大篇幅论述的是当时宋朝照搬三武一宗的理论大兴抑佛，从而达到剥夺寺产和振兴儒学的目的。这章如果展开的话，倒可以另成一书。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="543695852">
